#loginform installation
1. make sure the qgis installation dir structure follows:
	Qgis-install-dir-->{
			    Qgis-install-dir/bin-dir/qgis_executable_or_bat(for windows)_named_"qgis"
			    Qgis-install-dir/python-dir
			    Qgis other directories doesnt matter for the pluginFormInstallation		
			}
			  
2. copy the entire loginform folder("loginform" dir) into Qgis-install-dir/python-dir/
3. for windows installation it is possible to make a login.bat file and with the following lines in it:

@echo off
python ../python/loginform/__init__.py

4. save the login.bat file into the Qgis-install-dir/bin-dir
